Package com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms

The com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms package provides the interfaces for configuring the Key Provider Service.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Providers
    The Providers interface provides methods to create, update and delete Key Providers that handoff to key servers.

    ServiceStatus
    The ServiceStatus interface provides methods to get the Key Provider Service health status.

Package com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms Description

The com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms package provides the interfaces for configuring the Key Provider Service. It encapsulates one or more key servers and exposes Trusted Key Providers.
